dc_title_s: Chickasaw County, Iowa, 1941, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Image is a photoreduction of the mosaic created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol SQ. Form of individual image numbering: SQ-1B-[number], SQ-2B-[number], SQ-3B-[number], or SQ-4B-[number]."Flying completed August 30, 1941." Flown by Park Aerial Surveys, Inc. Louisville, Kentucky.
